        "title": "How to make your edit text alphanumeric? Android example",
        "body": "<p>Like if the user inputs only letters it will complain that the username must contain numbers and when the user inputs only numbers it will complain that username must contain letters.<\/p>\n\n<p>Here's my code, but it doesn't work properly.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>if(!username.matches(\"[a-zA-Z0-9]+\")){\n    Toast.makeText(this, \"Username must be alphanumeric\", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n    return;\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
