            "creation_date": 1500970731,
            "body": "<p>try this user Editext property <code>android:digits<\/code> so you can restrict user to enter only allowed charecter<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;EditText\n    android:layout_width=\"match_parent\"\n    android:layout_height=\"wrap_content\"\n    android:digits=\"ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWX1Z1234567890abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz \"/&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
